# Azenquoria Project Structure

This Flutter app follows a clean, layered architecture with clear separation of concerns:

## Main Entry Point
- [lib/main.dart](mdc:lib/main.dart) - App initialization, theme setup, and routing

## UI Layer
### Screens
- [lib/screens/journal_screen.dart](mdc:lib/screens/journal_screen.dart) - Journal entries and color theme selection
- [lib/screens/share_screen.dart](mdc:lib/screens/share_screen.dart) - QR code generation and sharing
- [lib/screens/breathe_screen.dart](mdc:lib/screens/breathe_screen.dart) - Breathing exercise modes and timers
- [lib/screens/settings_screen.dart](mdc:lib/screens/settings_screen.dart) - User settings and app guides

### Widgets
- [lib/widgets/record_card.dart](mdc:lib/widgets/record_card.dart) - Reusable card for journal/shared entries
- [lib/widgets/nav_bar.dart](mdc:lib/widgets/nav_bar.dart) - Bottom navigation bar
- [lib/widgets/color_picker.dart](mdc:lib/widgets/color_picker.dart) - Color theme selector

## Models
- [lib/models/journal_entry.dart](mdc:lib/models/journal_entry.dart) - Journal entry data structure
- [lib/models/breath_mode.dart](mdc:lib/models/breath_mode.dart) - Breathing exercise mode data
- [lib/models/share_card.dart](mdc:lib/models/share_card.dart) - Shared card with QR code data

## Services & Repositories
- [lib/services/journal_repository.dart](mdc:lib/services/journal_repository.dart) - Journal data storage
- [lib/services/breath_service.dart](mdc:lib/services/breath_service.dart) - Breathing exercise logic
- [lib/services/share_service.dart](mdc:lib/services/share_service.dart) - QR code generation and sharing
 